觀光業是澳大利亞經濟的重要部分。在2010/11財年，觀光業貢獻了澳大利亞2.5%的GDP<ref name="ABS1011">{{cite web|last=Australian Bureau of Statistics|title=Tourism Satellite Account 2010-11:Key Figures|url=http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/mf/5249.0?OpenDocument|accessdate=2016-02-02|archive-date=2018-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180615135014/http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/mf/5249.0?OpenDocument|dead-url=no}}</ref>截止2015年4月的一年內，有710萬外國遊客到訪澳大利亞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tourism.australia.com/statistics/arrivals.aspx|title=Visitor Arrivals Data|publisher=Tourism Australia|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905135526/http://www.tourism.australia.com/statistics/arrivals.aspx|archivedate=2015-09-05}}</ref>，產生513,700個工作崗位 。澳大利亞主要的旅遊目的地包括雪梨、墨爾本、昆士蘭的黃金海岸和大堡礁、烏魯魯巨岩、塔斯馬尼亞島等地區。澳洲獨特的野生動物也是澳洲觀光的一大賣點。澳洲最大的國際觀光客源是[[紐西蘭|紐西蘭]]，到訪率最高的州則是新南威爾士州、昆士蘭州和維多利亞州<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.clivehamilton.net.au/cms/media/documents/articles/Cashing_in_on_Koalas.pdf |title=Hamilton, Clive - Cashing In On Koalas |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2010-07-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110218165255/http://www.clivehamilton.net.au/cms/media/documents/articles/Cashing_in_on_Koalas.pdf |archivedate=2011-02-18 }}</ref>。此外，也有相當數量的背包客到訪澳洲，大多來自西歐（特別是英國）和北美。澳洲向18至30歲的青年開放打工度假的簽證，有不少西歐、加拿大和東亞青年取得澳洲的打工度假簽證<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.immi.gov.au/visitors/working-holiday/visa-options.htm |title=Visa Options - Working Holiday Makers - Visas & Immigration |publisher=Immi.gov.au |date=2008-10-29 |accessdate=2010-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100704073423/http://www.immi.gov.au/visitors/working-holiday/visa-options.htm |archive-date=2010-07-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。澳洲的外國遊客在以中國人遊客的平均消費金額最多<ref name="wrc">{{Cite news |url=http://www.smh.com.au/travel/travel-news/what-rich-chinese-tourists-want--and-where-theyre-going-to-get-it-20130606-2nryx.html |title=What rich Chinese tourists want - and where they're going to get it |author=Robert Upe |accessdate=6 July 2013 |date=6 June 2013 |newspaper=The Sydney Morning Herald |publisher=Fairfax Media |archive-date=2014-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140426223852/http://www.smh.com.au/travel/travel-news/what-rich-chinese-tourists-want--and-where-theyre-going-to-get-it-20130606-2nryx.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外，澳洲的國內旅遊市場的規模約有630億美元。

